OL,3,CCitizens Advice giving 'crisis
OL,4,Csupport' every 30 seconds ahead of
OL,5,Cbill rises
OL,7,FCitizens Advice has warned it is
OL,8,Falready giving "crisis support" every
OL,9,F30 seconds ahead of household bills
OL,10,Fincluding council tax and water rising
OL,11,Ffrom April.
OL,13,FThe advisory service said it had
OL,14,Fhelped more than 51,000 people with
OL,15,Fcrisis support so far this year, with
OL,16,Frenters, disabled people and single
OL,17,Fparents among those most likely to
OL,18,Fseek assistance.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@_O]
