OL,3,CCitizens Advice giving 'crisis
OL,4,Csupport' every 30 seconds ahead of
OL,5,Cbill rises
OL,7,FWhen broader cost-of-living issues
OL,8,Flike energy bills and council tax
OL,9,Farrears were included, the number of
OL,10,Fpeople seeking help reached 175,000.
OL,12,FThe charity warned the figures
OL,13,Findicated how many household budgets
OL,14,Fhad already "gone beyond breaking
OL,15,Fpoint".
OL,17,FOf those the charity had helped,
OL,18,Faverage debt had reached a record
OL,19,F#9,500, up 12% on last year.
OL,26,@vD@MOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774555873
OL,3,CCitizens Advice giving 'crisis
OL,4,Csupport' every 30 seconds ahead of
OL,5,Cbill rises
OL,7,FOn average, more than a third of this
OL,8,Fdebt (42%) was arrears on essential
OL,9,Fbills such as energy and council tax.
OL,11,FCitizens Advice said it anticipated
OL,12,Fthe number of those in debt would rise
OL,13,Ffurther, with global instability
OL,14,Fthreatening more price shocks and
OL,15,Fessential bills going up in April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
