CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774555873
OL,3,CCitizens Advice giving 'crisis
OL,4,Csupport' every 30 seconds ahead of
OL,5,Cbill rises
OL,7,FIt said government moves including
OL,8,Fscrapping the two-child benefit limit
OL,9,Fand bringing down energy bills from
OL,10,FApril were "steps in the right
OL,11,Fdirection" but warned more help was
OL,12,Fneeded.
OL,14,FIt is calling for better-targeted
OL,15,Fsupport for those who are struggling
OL,16,Fthe most with energy bills, help with
OL,17,Frent costs and speeding up action to
OL,18,Fget people out of debt.
OL,26,@rD@LOUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
