OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774555873
OL,3,CCitizens Advice giving 'crisis
OL,4,Csupport' every 30 seconds ahead of
OL,5,Cbill rises
OL,7,FCitizens Advice chief executive Dame
OL,8,FClare Moriarty said: "Our data reveals
OL,9,Fthe scale of the problem facing people
OL,10,F` households are buckling under cost-
OL,11,Fof-living pressures, and too many are
OL,12,Freaching crisis.
OL,14,F"Every day our advisers see people at
OL,15,Fbreaking point, with nowhere left to
OL,16,Fcut back and debts spinning out of
OL,17,Fcontrol. Now, worrying global events
OL,18,Flook likely to bring fresh challenges
OL,19,Fto already stretched budgets.
OL,26,@pD@VOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774555873
OL,3,CCitizens Advice giving 'crisis
OL,4,Csupport' every 30 seconds ahead of
OL,5,Cbill rises
OL,7,F"That is why the Government must give
OL,8,Fa lifeline to the households
OL,9,Fstruggling the most. This should
OL,10,Finclude help with rent costs, better-
OL,11,Ftargeted support with energy bills, as
OL,12,Fwell as measures to tackle record-
OL,13,Fbreaking levels of debt."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@YO]
